{
  "id": "adv_love_2305_08_03",
  "title": "Episode 8 Part 3",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――三月八日　高校卒業式の日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――March 8th\n at high sch commencement",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "choice_selection",
      "choices": [
        {
          "text": "告白する",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_03-koh010.m4a",
              "text": "好きです、付き合って下さい",
              "translations": {
                "en": "I like you. Would you go out with me?",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 84.9333395443,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_trouble-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 88.0333364925
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rei",
              "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
              "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_03-rei007.m4a",
              "text": "え……突然何……？",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Huh…? What's all this sudden…?",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 88.0333364925,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_03-koh011.m4a",
              "text": "俺、やっぱり怜のことが\n好きなんだなって思って\n前みたいに仲良くしてほしい",
              "translations": {
                "en": "I've come to realize that\nI still like you‚ Rei.\nI want us to be as close as\nwe used to be.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 93.4666677913,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rei",
              "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
              "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_03-rei008.m4a",
              "text": "ごめんなさい、無理よ\nその言葉、もう少し早く聞きたかったわ……",
              "translations": {
                "en": "I'm sorry‚ but that's not possible.\nI wish I'd heard those words\na little earlier…",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 100.7000057023,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "stop",
              "startTime": 108.2666764379
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rei",
              "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
              "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_03-rei009.m4a",
              "text": "私も{user}のこと\n好きだったわ\nでも、恋ってタイミングが一番大事なの",
              "translations": {
                "en": "I also liked you‚\n{user}.\nBut… timing is crucial in love.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 108.9666810155,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_sad-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 113.3666677277
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rei",
              "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
              "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_03-rei010.m4a",
              "text": "今の私は\nもうこれっぽっちもあなたに好意はない\nさようなら",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Right now‚ I don't have\nany feelings for you at all.\nGoodbye.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 118.366687119,
              "sfxList": []
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "見送る",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_sad-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 125.3333512424
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_03-koh012.m4a",
              "text": "ああ、それじゃあ、また……",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Yeah‚ then… see you…",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 125.3333512424,
              "sfxList": [
                {
                  "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
                  "delay": 3183.3134334999895
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "unknown",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": null,
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_03-koh013.m4a",
              "text": "（俺は、怜の背中を静かに見送った\n勉強は得意なはずなのに……）",
              "translations": {
                "en": "（I silently watched Rei leave.\nI should be good at studying‚ but…）",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 129.9666672823,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "unknown",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": null,
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_03-koh014.m4a",
              "text": "（怜の心を取り戻す方程式の解は\n見つからなかった。どこでミスを\nしたのかさえ……分からない……）",
              "translations": {
                "en": "（I couldn't find the solution\nto winning back Rei's heart.\nI don't even know…\nwhere I went wrong…）",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 136.166666265,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "unknown",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": null,
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_03-koh015.m4a",
              "text": "（ただ一つだけ、確信したことがある\n今の怜は俺が嫌いだってこと）",
              "translations": {
                "en": "（There's only one thing I'm sure of\nRei dislikes me now.）",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 144.7666550752,
              "sfxList": []
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "なんでこんなことに",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_trouble-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 152.2666428681
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_03-koh016.m4a",
              "text": "俺達、なんでこんなことに\nなっちゃったんだろうな\n結構いい感じだったじゃないか……",
              "translations": {
                "en": "How did we\nend up like this?\nIt was pretty going well…",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 152.2666428681,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rei",
              "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
              "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_03-rei011.m4a",
              "text": "は……？　何言ってるの？",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Huh…?\nWhat are you talking about?",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 159.3999721325,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_03-koh017.m4a",
              "text": "テーマパーク行ったりとか\n一緒に勉強したりとか……\n楽しかったじゃないか……",
              "translations": {
                "en": "We went to the theme park together‚\nand we studied together…\nDidn't you have fun…?",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 163.6666286266,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rei",
              "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
              "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_03-rei012.m4a",
              "text": "あなたは楽しかったかもしれないけれど\n私は別に……楽しくなかったわ",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Maybe you enjoyed it‚\nbut I certainly…\ndidn't have fun at all.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 170.3999578909,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_03-koh018.m4a",
              "text": "そ、そんな……",
              "translations": {
                "en": "I-I see…",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 178.7666296438,
              "sfxList": [
                {
                  "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
                  "delay": 11433.373451600004
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rei",
              "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
              "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_03-rei013.m4a",
              "text": "何を勘違いしていたのか知らないけれど……\nもう行くわね。さようなら",
              "translations": {
                "en": "I don't know what\nyou've been misunderstanding‚\nbut… I'm leaving now. Goodbye.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 181.866626592,
              "sfxList": []
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 1.6333333771
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 1.6333333771
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（怜からのテーマパークの誘いを断ってから\n俺達は学校でも全く会話をしなくなった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Ever since I turned down\nRei's invitation to the theme park‚\nwe stopped talking‚ even at school.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.5333333771,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（俺、なんかしてしまったかな……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Did I do something wrong…?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.3333331864,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 12.5666663926
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 12.5666663926
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（卒業したらもう会うこともなくなるし……\n話し掛けてみるか）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Once we graduate‚ we won't see\neach other anymore…\nShould I try talking to her?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.5666663926,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5843.333651099998
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 17.8666667104
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "おい、怜。久しぶり！\n最近どう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ Rei. Long time no see!\nHow have you been lately?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.8999978186,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 22.6999976915
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_03-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "別に……普通よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nothing special…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.6999976915,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 25.9666643581
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "普通って……卒業後の進路はどうするんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nothing spe… So‚ what are\nyour plans after graduation?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.9666643581,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "再オーディション、ダメだったんだろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You didn't pass the re-audition‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.599998073,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 33.6333331865
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_03-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "自分に才能が無いことは分かったし\nキャストになる夢は諦めることにしたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I realized I lack talent‚ so I've\ngiven up on my dream of becoming\na cast member.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.6333331865,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_03-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "東橋大学は落ちてしまったし\n滑り止めで受かった地方の医学部に\n行くつもり",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I failed to get into East Hashi\nUniversity‚ so I'm planning to attend\na local medical school\nas a fallback.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.9333311519,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.2000001074
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
